This week on the Major Issues Podcast we dig into Peach Momoko’s Ultimate X-Men. We break down the reimagined cast of mutants, from Hisako and Mei to Tsubasa, Kanon, and the Shadow King, while unpacking the arcs, themes, and cultural influence driving the story. We also highlight the striking artwork that sets this book apart and explore why it might be the boldest entry in Marvel’s new Ultimate line.

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

